  "title": "A Dangerous Historical Trip",
  "article_text": "Tonight, a group of scientists will travel onto a historical battlefield to study old bombs. They must be careful because the bombs are dangerous and can hurt people. Moreover, the army opposes their trip, so they choose a different route. The council belongs to the city and makes rules for safety. Each scientist wants to taste the excitement of discovery, but the danger is real. They pack their vehicle with tools and check every branch of their plan. The bomb squad will bind the old bombs to decrease the risk. This historical site is more comfortable than usual for their work. They carefully follow the rules and do not oppose the council's advice. The fashion of old bombs shocks everyone, but the scientists feel no fear.",
